<CHAPTER LBL="2"><TITLE><XREFTARGET ID="37736">Planning a Network</TITLE><PARAGRAPH>This chapter contains common-sense approaches to planning the physical and logical aspects of your network environment. The information contained in this chapter should be read before you set up a new network or integrate into an existing network. </PARAGRAPH>
<PARAGRAPH>This chapter contains the following sections:</PARAGRAPH>
<BULLETLIST><BULLET><PARAGRAPH><XREF IDREF="74943" TYPE="TITLE">&ldquo;Planning the Physical Network&rdquo;</XREF></PARAGRAPH>
</BULLET>
